      "widgets_values": [
        "# ⬅ THE MODE SWITCH\n\n## 1) storyboard\n### One picture per scene, fast. Look before you spend render time.\n\n## 2) storyboard to movie\n### THE movie button. Same hero, same places, a fresh camera angle every scene.\n\n## 3) storyboard to movie (exact frames)\n### Strict: every scene starts on the exact picture you approved.\n\n## 4) quick movie (scenes independent)\n### Skips the storyboard. Every scene invents its own look.\n\n# Storyboard first → approve → switch to 2 → Queue"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
